com.davidsoergel.stats
Class DistributionXYSeries

java.lang.Object
  com.davidsoergel.stats.DistributionXYSeries

public class DistributionXYSeries
extends Object

Stores a set of y values for each x value, allowing computation of mean, standard deviation, and quantiles for each x.

The reason we don't extend SimpleXYSeries is to avoid redundant storage of the points
